			<view isee:template_view="template:3" isee:name="Intro" background="white" page_width="1066" page_height="600" zoom="115" home_view="true" type="interface">
				<style>
					<isee:stacked_container item_spacing="0" corner_radius="4" selected_item_color="black" selected_item_background="white" item_background="#DDDDDD" transparent_bg="false"/>
				</style>
				<text_box x="14.2189" y="102.292" width="575.301" height="374.433">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;,&apos;sans-serif&apos;; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD) is a progressive disease involving gradual loss of kidney function. It is often symptomless in its early stages. &lt;/span&gt;CKD is classified into five stages, based on eGFR and ACR. This simulation tool is limited to CKD stages 3a to 5.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;System dynamics modelling is an effective method for simulating the progression of chronic disease and the impact that one or more interventions can have on the prevalent population.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;The tool will simulate the number of people (aged 18 and over) likely to have CKD up to the end of 2035, for each diagnosis state and CKD stage. The tool also allows the user to understand the impact of applying interventions, such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;	- primary preventions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;	- improved diagnosis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;	- increased usage of medication&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;and includes elements of costing, which will allow cost comparisons between different interventions (high level only).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;This version of the model is pre-populated with the estimates and projections of NHS regions and England. Use the selector in the top-right corner to choose a region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;The Storyboard give more detail around the logic, limitations, assumptions of the model.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;The Simulator allows you to explore the effect of interventions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<button background="#587FC1" font_weight="bold" font_color="white" border_width="thin" border_style="none" corner_radius="5" isee:flat="true" label="Go to Simulator" isee:tooltip="" x="915.272" y="197.108" width="135" height="30">
					<actions>
						<action target="interface:2">navigate</action>
					</actions>
				</button>
				<button background="#587FC1" font_weight="bold" font_color="white" border_width="thin" border_style="none" corner_radius="5" isee:flat="true" label="Go to Storyboard" isee:tooltip="" x="915.272" y="151.174" width="135" height="30">
					<actions>
						<action target="story" view="0" story="249">navigate</action>
					</actions>
				</button>
				<text_box x="15.1818" y="72.6588" width="260" height="20.6362">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Arial&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Introduction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<text_box font_family="segoe ui" x="690.055" y="139.149" width="225" height="54.2642">The storyboard gives a high-level overview of the model and its structure, and explains the logic behind the model. 

</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="702.651" y="495.637" width="243.795" height="55">Use these buttons to run the model in steps or all the way to the end. You can change settings between steps and then run the model for a period to see the impact.</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="873.033" y="378.232" width="175" height="34.9459">Hover over/click the Info button for more detail on how to use the feature</text_box>
				<graphics_frame fill="none" x="839.723" y="427.643" width="35" height="30">
					<image width="36" height="39" size_to_parent="true" isee:transparency="0" isee:fixed_aspect_ratio="true">data:image/png;base64,</image>
				</graphics_frame>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="873.723" y="439.166" width="175" height="33.5227">Reset an individual input to its default value</text_box>
				<text_box z_index="6" background="#2C2825" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="4.50734" y="495.637" width="209.989" height="55">Grey buttons are reset buttons:
&apos;Clear Graphs&apos; - clears the charts shown
&apos;Reset Inputs&apos; -  restores all inputs to their defaults.</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" text_align="center" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="369.702" y="495.637" width="213.244" height="55">Use these buttons to run the model to the end. You can pause along the way and adjust values. </text_box>
				<isee:annotation transparent="true" isee:flat="true" popup_background_color="white" launcher_label="" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="845.533" y="368.132" width="25" height="25">
					<launcher_image width="96" height="96" size_to_parent="true">data:image/png;base64,</launcher_image>
					<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="783.5" y="373" width="203" height="117.506">
						<text>A pop-up with more information will appear when you hover over the Info button.

Click outside the pop-up to return to the main screen.</text>
					</popup>
				</isee:annotation>
				<text_box font_family="segoe ui" x="690.055" y="196.406" width="225" height="40.0613">Go to the simulator to explore
</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" text_align="center" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="980.138" y="495.637" width="66.0202" height="55">Export the values of a run to csv</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" text_align="center" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="222.125" y="495.637" width="142.633" height="55">&apos;Run live&apos; allows you to see changes made to inputs immediately, across the whole simulation period.</text_box>
				<text_box font_style="italic" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="11pt" x="788.855" y="100.085" width="265" height="39.0642">Select NHS region from the dropdown menu - this will carry through to all pages 

</text_box>
				<graphics_frame fill="none" x="852.341" y="243.816" width="197.931" height="111.034">
					<video>C:/Users/Sally.Thompson.MLCSU/OneDrive - Midlands and Lancashire CSU/Documents/FlashIntegro/VideoEditor/CKD demo v3.mp4</video>
				</graphics_frame>
				<text_box x="690.055" y="260.828" width="127.586" height="77.0111">Video walk-through (click the open square to open in a new window)</text_box>
				<isee:annotation launcher_label="" show_by_default="true" hide_launcher="true" launch_on_hover="false" x="349.758" y="255.2">
					<popup x="126.255" y="89.8" width="563.8" height="389.6">
						<text>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;**** New Release ****&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:&apos;Arial&apos;; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;June 2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;The model has been refreshed with CVD Prevent data up to the end of 2025, and UKRR data to the end of 2024.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Flow rates have been re-calibrated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Results from the previous release of the model should not be compared directly with results from this release.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;More information in the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Changelog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; (via the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;More info&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; tab)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;Click to hide this message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
					</popup>
				</isee:annotation>
			</view>
			<view isee:template_view="template:2" isee:name="Calibration" background="white" page_width="1066" page_height="600" zoom="115" type="interface">
				<style>
					<isee:stacked_container item_spacing="0" corner_radius="4" selected_item_color="black" selected_item_background="white" item_background="#DDDDDD" transparent_bg="false"/>
				</style>
				<text_box x="642.828" y="124.929" width="409.144" height="308.508">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;The model has been calibrated by adjusting the flow rates (between states and also mortality in each state) so that the model (blue line) matches known values (red dashed line). The time period for the calibration is 2021-Q4 to 2024-Q2.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;The data sources for the known values are CVD Prevent and the UK Renal Registry. Findings from Inside CKD are used to split prevalence into stages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Diagnosis rates and the mortality factor at each stage were also calibrated:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;	- diagnosis rates at each stage were calibrated such that the total diagnosis rate matched the high-level diagnosis rate (see page 1 of the storyboard)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;	- the scale factor applied to mortality rates at each stage were calibrated such that the overall mortality rate matched &apos;CVD all-cause&apos; mortality from CVD Prevent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<stacked_container x="-9.9454" y="86.5672" width="300" height="225">
					<graph font_size="10pt" isee:transparent="false" isee:hide_border="true" axis_title_font_size="9pt" width="300" height="225" type="time_series" show_grid="false" isee:tick_type="none" include_units_in_legend="false" plot_numbers="false" isee:label_pie_slices="false" isee:show_pie_borders="true" num_x_grid_lines="0" num_y_grid_lines="0" num_x_labels="3" num_y_labels="3" title="Undiagnosed Stage 3-5" isee:fill_intensity="0.1" to="2026" from="2021.75" isee:allow_zero_axis="true" left_axis_multi_scale="false" left_axis_auto_scale="true" left_include_units="true" right_axis_multi_scale="false" right_axis_auto_scale="true" right_include_units="true">
