				<text_box x="15.6667" y="95.6828" width="288" height="162.662">The annual incidence figures, cost of medications and difference in costs (primary prevention and meds) from the baseline can be used as an input to the linked KRT model.

Run a scenario within this model, then use the Export button to export as a csv file. Choose a suitable name when saving the file. Paste the values from 2023 to 2035 into the Renal Modelling Input File.</text_box>
			</view>
