			<isee:stories>
				<isee:story uid="249" name="ckd progression">
					<view isee:template_view="template:5" background="white" page_width="1066" page_height="600" zoom="165" type="interface">
						<style>
							<isee:stacked_container item_spacing="0" corner_radius="4" selected_item_color="black" selected_item_background="white" item_background="#DDDDDD" transparent_bg="false"/>
						</style>
						<isee:model_view x="0" y="0" width="1066" height="600" isee:locked="true" zoom="1" center_x="533" center_y="398" locked_view="true" transparent="true" use_visible_list="true" show_ltm_table="false">
							<model name="Top-Level"/>
							<isee:visible_list>
								<entity name='"diag_4-5_mort"'/>
								<entity name="diag_3_mort"/>
								<entity name='"S4-5_to_KRT"'/>
								<entity name="undiagnosed"/>
								<entity name='"S3_to_4-5"'/>
								<entity name="CKD_3"/>
								<entity name="diag_KRT_mort"/>
								<item uid="247"/>
								<item uid="248"/>
								<item uid="148"/>
								<entity name='"CKD_4-5_not_KRT"'/>
								<item uid="13"/>
								<entity name="diagnosed"/>
								<entity name="diagnosis_rate_p_h_th"/>
								<entity name="new_diagnoses"/>
								<entity name="KRT"/>
								<entity name="exp_incidence"/>
								<entity name="incidence_rate_p_h_th"/>
								<entity name="all_undiag_mort"/>
								<entity name="ons_pop"/>
								<entity name="all_diag_mort"/>
							</isee:visible_list>
							<isee:highlight_list/>
						</isee:model_view>
						<text_box x="18.2608" y="143.478" width="260" height="256.521">The prevalence of CKD increases with age. This model only considers the population of people aged 35 and over, and the more advance stages of CKD - stage 3a to stage 5.

In the simplest terms, each year a proportion of the population of interest develop CKD but are undiagnosed. Each year, a proportion of the undiagnosed population are diagnosed. A small proportion of this group will, in time, develop a need for kidney replacement therapy (KRT).

Hover over the annotation buttons for a high-level description of how people flow through the disease states.


</text_box>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="1. developing CKD" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="376.304" y="128.478" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="443.457" y="189.633" width="165.261" height="93.0435">
								<text>Each year, a proportion of the population (incidence rate) develop CKD.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="2. initial diagnosis state" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="579.347" y="149.782" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="608.793" y="207.745" width="105.021" height="61.6021">
								<text>New cases are undiagnosed</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="3. diagnosis" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="769.347" y="228.478" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="788.674" y="302.677" width="165.261" height="93.0435">
								<text>Each year, a proportion of the undiagnosed stock are diagnosed with CKD (stage 3a to 5). </text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="4. mortality" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="777.608" y="88.0435" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="755.195" y="163.112" width="184.391" height="92.1739">
								<text>Regardless of cause, a proportion of both undiagnosed and diagnosed will die each year.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="5. determining incidence and diagnosis rates" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="455.434" y="385" width="145.652" height="42.1739">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="416.695" y="438.043" width="247.87" height="143.478">
								<text>The incidence rate is determined by matching the model&apos;s values for undiagnosed and diagnosed with known values.
The data sources for the known values are the Health Survey for England 2016 and 2022, QOF, and CVD Prevent.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<button transparent="true" label="" isee:tooltip="" x="1020.93" y="554.286" width="30" height="30">
