						<text_box x="33.913" y="272.174" width="234.783" height="153.043">A staged CKD model is shown here. 
The incidence rate derived in the previous step is used as the &apos;undiagnosed new cases&apos;.

All flows between stages and diagnosis states are rates, proportional to the stock they are flowing from. (rate per hundred thousand per year)

 


</text_box>
						<graphics_frame fill="none" x="280" y="69.6335" width="561.739" height="75.6522">
							<image width="2589" height="224" size_to_parent="true" isee:transparency="0" isee:fixed_aspect_ratio="true">data:image/png;base64,</image>
						</graphics_frame>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="undiagnosed and worsening" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="464.412" y="119.782" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="438.521" y="198.695" width="165.261" height="93.0435">
								<text>All new cases are deemed to be stage 3. Whilst undiagnosed this can worsen, to stage 4-5.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="diagnosis" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="454.412" y="271.521" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="436.347" y="316.521" width="165.261" height="47.8261">
								<text>Diagnosis can occur at any stage of the disease.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
						<isee:annotation launcher_label="mortality" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="472.783" y="533.261" width="120.435" height="40.4348">
							<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="699.543" y="488.329" width="184.391" height="92.1739">
								<text>Regardless of cause, a proportion of each stage/diagnosis state will die each year.</text>
							</popup>
						</isee:annotation>
